Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:16.11,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur2.5\pos(960,800)\3c&HFFFFFF&}家有女友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.05,0:26:08.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,對不起啦 我愛你
